high_descs: Go forward and to the right of the coffee table, then turn to face the side of the table.
Get the cellphone from the table.
Go to your left, to the brown upholstered chair at the corner of the rug.
Put the cellphone on the right front corner of the seat of the chair.
Turn left and go the right end of the TV stand, then turn to face it.
Pick up the cellphone from the left corner of the stand.
Turn left and cross the room, back to the brown chair in the left far corner of the room.
Place the cellphone to the left of the other cellphone on the seat of the chair.
anns.task_desc: Move two cellphones to the seat of a brown upholstered chair.

high_descs: Turn and go to the coffee table.

Put the cell phone on the cloth chair.
